title: Reflexive - Flower Paradise - New Match 3 - Wendy99
description:
Flower Paradise - 36.65 MB


Paradise awaits in this fun filled flower matching game! Match 18 unique flower types as you 
build your own Japanese, Hawaiian and French gardens. Play traditional Match 3 puzzles or try the 
innovative Box Clear Mode! Customize your gardens with birds, butterflies, landscaping and more 
as you unlock new flowers and features. Once you have your garden exactly the way you like it, 

you can turn it into wallpaper for your desktop, or even an animated screensaver!
